div.p: After the initial setup, the focus will drive new opportunities to document related metadata. For instance, assuming the trigger is regulation (ex. GDPR) and the focus is put on documenting data usage. The requirement to classify the data for privacy purpose is an opportunity to setup the data glossary as well if it does not exist.

div.p: Depending on the requirements, the focus will be put on a set of metadata to start :

ul.li: Usage (data processing activities, data transfer, data recipient...)
Rule & Policy (Business data quality rule, data policy...)
